Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.22,0:00:05.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那麼今天的課就上到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.92,0:00:07.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為現在白晝的時間變短了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.76,0:00:10.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要在天黑之前回家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.22,0:00:13.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞  去玩吧  去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.31,0:00:13.28,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}去玩什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.15,0:00:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻就把什麼都稱作plasma了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.61,0:00:21.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.86,0:00:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.81,0:00:24.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.35,0:00:26.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吃車站前的那個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.75,0:00:27.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.68,0:00:28.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:30.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個  啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.13,0:00:33.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  美緒也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.27,0:00:36.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  已經先回去了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:37.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.49,0:00:40.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.39,0:00:47.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒回答就跑出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.25,0:00:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣會不會對相生同學不太好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.68,0:00:55.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能再稍微像普通的女孩子一點來打招呼就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.22,0:00:58.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…我叫東雲名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.02,0:01:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個  是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.77,0:01:04.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這個發條是…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.65,0:02:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為附近的咖啡店重新翻修了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.45,0:02:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就試著進去看看了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:02:59.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.24,0:03:02.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問您要點什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意式濃咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.43,0:03:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要Tea的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.47,0:03:16.96,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(90,300)\fad(400,00)\bord20\shad0\be20\3c&HFFFFFF&}日\N常\N之\N64
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:19.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.61,0:03:22.16,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}以下出現的都是咖啡的術語，Tall代表標準杯。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.61,0:03:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意式濃咖啡的Tall杯對嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.35,0:03:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tall？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.78,0:03:25.62,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tall和透的發音相同。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.78,0:03:25.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.86,0:03:27.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,T代表透？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.63,0:03:28.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈哈  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.13,0:03:32.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  我還在想喝份意式濃咖啡的Tea的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.20,0:03:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那麼就給我意式濃咖啡的T的Small吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:43.55,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Short代表小杯，和Small差不多。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:43.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是想點意式濃咖啡的Short嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:55.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我那個Small的Short杯就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.07,0:03:57.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:03:59.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就是意式濃咖啡的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.58,0:04:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:04.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡有分熱的和冰的兩種
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:06.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就給我熱的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  如果是熱的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.70,0:04:11.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小還有分…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:19.48,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Solo為單份濃縮，Doppio為雙份濃縮。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:19.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Solo和Doppio兩種
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.97,0:04:21.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DoDoDoDoDo…Doppio！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:22.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Doppio？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Doppio又是什麼鬼東西啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.76,0:04:27.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Doppio…Doppio
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:29.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Doppio到底是什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.88,0:04:31.66,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,230)}今日的咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.02,0:04:35.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了  我差點忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.30,0:04:38.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來是想點這個今日的咖啡的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.14,0:04:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:47.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日的咖啡就是意式濃咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:51.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:54.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那您是要Solo…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:01.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是Doppio的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.84,0:05:05.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Doppio…Doppio…Doppio的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:18.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說…說的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.49,0:05:27.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那就請你幫我選個適合的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.48,0:05:29.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:42.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:44.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是您的意式濃咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.79,0:05:58.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好小…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.62,0:06:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好苦啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:19.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.50,0:06:28.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:32.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後還是去自動售貨機買好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.07,0:06:43.83,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,350)\fad(400,400)}投\N球\N接\N球\N練\N習
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:44.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我買了棒球手套作為外孫小實的生日禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.73,0:06:47.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外公  我要丟了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:48.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  小實
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.87,0:06:51.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像隔那麼遠的話是丟不到的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.79,0:06:53.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然這麼高興
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.86,0:06:55.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然外孫就是可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:57.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要丟了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.34,0:07:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊  你就投個痛快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:05.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是今天就向外孫展示一下我帥氣的一面…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.18,0:07:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sinker…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.35,0:07:16.03,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(670,330)\fad(400,0)\bord10\shad0\be30\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs30}T\Ni\Nc\No\Nm\Na\Nr\Nt
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.21,0:07:16.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}悶絕！又熱又燙大廚心血來潮！雞肉棒--50日元
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.93,0:07:15.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:16.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請給我一根這個悶絕又熱又燙大廚心血來潮的雞肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.97,0:07:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人  您就饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.65,0:07:42.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了  小次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.68,0:07:44.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.96,0:07:46.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不趕快的話  報名就結束…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:47.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.22,0:07:50.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐…祐子  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.52,0:07:54.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼怎麼了啊  班會結束後我才發現你不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.71,0:07:56.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.61,0:07:59.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也不遲哦  一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.25,0:08:00.51,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}不  我接下來還有點事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.67,0:08:04.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  那個  那個說起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.23,0:08:07.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  什麼啊  你那扭捏的語氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:10.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  怎麼說呢  嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.09,0:08:11.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:12.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微打擾下好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.19,0:08:15.86,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(60,300)\fad(400,0)\bord10\shad0\be30\3c&HFFFFFF&}日\N常\N之\N65
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:17.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:19.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.63,0:08:20.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.67,0:08:23.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  祐子  你幹了什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.11,0:08:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺地就道歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:29.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  我也嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.45,0:08:31.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然被人道歉什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.26,0:08:32.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:34.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是您有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.67,0:08:38.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是最近經常有人用假幣投入自動售貨機
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想問問你們有沒有看到可疑的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:42.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒  你有看到過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.96,0:08:45.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊我不經常來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:47.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據目擊者的資訊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:51.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人是提著紅色條紋的米色手提袋的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.48,0:08:53.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能會有這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.78,0:08:58.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  這個不尋常的反應到底是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.49,0:09:00.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有嗎  你有帶假幣嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.36,0:09:03.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  怎麼會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.99,0:09:05.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  開什麼玩笑嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:10.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  為什麼自己伸手等著被捕啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:13.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  你有帶假鈔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.83,0:09:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能  她只是擺出架勢  這樣無論哪兒飛來的排球都能接住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:20.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  美緒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.92,0:09:26.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  算了  首先為了確認一下  就讓我看下你們兩人的包裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.90,0:09:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  請看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.61,0:09:29.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  美緒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.93,0:09:34.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交出來了  她把假鈔交出來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:39.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都完了  沒想到她真的有假鈔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.02,0:09:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請收下並且放過我吧
