Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.83,0:13:46.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  這個與其說是擦  倒不如說是拉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.89,0:13:49.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子  借我橡皮擦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.86,0:13:51.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣也沒有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.65,0:13:53.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.16,0:13:55.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜吧  哪邊？
