Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.29,0:14:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧來吧  請隨便調查
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.97,0:14:11.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好燙燙燙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.35,0:14:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不算不算  不能用攻擊招數的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.98,0:14:16.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣要One pena呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.47,0:14:17.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One pena是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.76,0:14:19.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是One penalty
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.76,0:14:19.33,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(360,335)\fs25}一次懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:21.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One penalty會發生什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:25.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請我喝23瓶果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.37,0:14:27.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還懷恨在心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.29,0:14:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  祐子  吃乾脆面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.75,0:14:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀自在菩薩  行深般若波羅蜜多時  照下五…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}源自般若波羅密多心經
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好危險  差點就上套了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.85,0:14:43.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是照下五  是照見五
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:45.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為能行的呢
