Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:56.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  被算計了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:14:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼祐子  把橡皮擦給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:15:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好好好  給  如你所願
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,角色橡皮擦  技能篇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.70,0:15:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.19,0:15:11.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然角色橡皮擦擦不乾淨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.05,0:15:11.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.83,0:15:13.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.91,0:15:14.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:21.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃果然是個機器人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.66,0:15:23.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我差不多一點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃很討厭這麼說她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:26.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  為什麼討厭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.79,0:15:28.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機器人不是很厲害嗎
