Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  東雲  東雲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:34.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.08,0:16:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東雲研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.94,0:16:42.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  原來是研究所啊  好帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.47,0:16:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了  有人在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.12,0:16:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  沒人在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.97,0:16:52.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.91,0:16:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  讓你久等了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:58.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎怎怎怎…怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.81,0:17:01.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼相生同學會來我們家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.52,0:17:06.33,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}是  啊  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:03.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果讓她和博士撞見的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:05.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是機器人的事實就會暴露無遺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.45,0:17:07.78,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}咦  名乃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.19,0:17:08.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.83,0:17:09.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}名乃在裡面
