Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.36,0:17:12.35,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}是的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.39,0:17:14.59,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}哇 進來進來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.89,0:17:13.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等下  也許她只是來送資料之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:15.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這樣  就在玄關…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:15.87,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.04,0:17:17.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}請進
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.24,0:17:18.59,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}啊  請不必張羅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:19.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.71,0:17:24.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇哦……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.89,0:17:28.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然進來了那就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:31.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在博士胡說八道之前把事情辦完…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  肚子餓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:34.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:35.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.77,0:17:38.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的聲音是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:40.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫阪本的貓  會說話哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.80,0:17:42.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.36,0:17:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:45.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼可能有那種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.47,0:17:48.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪…阪本先生  請學貓叫  喵一個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.99,0:17:50.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  為什麼我現在要…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.88,0:17:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵一個  阪本先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.18,0:17:53.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵…喵……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.08,0:17:55.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  只是普通的貓對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.99,0:17:56.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.38,0:17:59.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本先生  因為今天有客人在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.75,0:18:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就去外面玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.74,0:18:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:12.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:15.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有好好地打個招呼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.30,0:18:16.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是相生祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.75,0:18:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你是名乃的妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.00,0:18:22.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  我是博士  是我製造了名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.97,0:18:24.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你製造的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.92,0:18:26.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  這麼小卻這麼厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.09,0:18:29.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士就是博士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.93,0:18:31.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  相生同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.91,0:18:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個孩子是親戚的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.21,0:18:35.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她爸媽都要工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.25,0:18:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很晚也回不了家  所以要我幫忙照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.25,0:18:40.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  對吧  吶吶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:41.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
